2. THE FUNDAMENTAL INSIGHT: SIMPLICITY AS STRATEGY

The ST-T1024 standard was designed for hardware efficiency. This is not an accident—it is the core strategic advantage.

What ST-T1024 eliminates:

Feature Why Eliminated Impact on Silicon
Floating-point multipliers Ternary logic {-1, 0, +1} ~90% reduction in arithmetic logic
Stochastic sampling Temperature = 0.0 No random number generators needed
Massive DRAM arrays 75% ROM / 25% SRAM Memory footprint: 0.7 MB vs 14 GB
Cloud dependency Air-gapped execution No network interfaces required
Active cooling Power gating to 0V No thermal management overhead

The result: An ST-T1024 ASIC is orders of magnitude simpler than a modern GPU or cloud AI accelerator. This simplicity translates directly to lower risk, lower cost, and faster time-to-market.

The accessibility insight: Because the architecture is simple, the implementation process is straightforward. Any medium engineer can execute it. The tools exist. The knowledge is public. The path is clear.

