6. THE CERTIFICATION ADVANTAGE

ST-T1024 is designed for functional safety certification: ISO 26262 (automotive), IEC 61508 (industrial), DO-178C (aerospace), and IEC 62304 (medical).

How silicon accelerates certification:

Requirement Emulator Silicon
Determinism Simulated Physical—WCET guaranteed
Traceability Logged FSM states are hardware-observable
Freedom from Interference Simulated Tile isolation is physically enforced
ASIL Decomposition Planned Hardware-independent tiles enable easy decomposition

The key: Silicon provides the physical proof required for certification bodies (TÜV, UL) to grant SIL/ASIL ratings.

